{"tid":888974,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇ching玩過hackathon可以分享下?","createTime":"2018-11-04T08:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T08:34:31.000Z","uid":147785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"10fe247ce64ba1ccd583460bee85d6a26959df8f","tid":888974,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T08:03:51.000Z","msg":"大概要咩程度先唔會做雷友?<br />\n<br />\n想試但又怕唔夠料<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eventbrite.com/e/techcrunch-international-city-event-hong-kong-hackathon-tickets-51448231044?aff=erelexpmlt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eventbrite.com%2Fe%2Ftechcrunch-international-city-event-hong-kong-hackathon-tickets-51448231044%3Faff%3Derelexpmlt&d=8dA%2FicDEPNKOZgrjHyrZlgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=dfeec538\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eventbrite.com/e/techcrunch-international-city-event-hong-kong-hackathon-tickets-51448231044?aff=erelexpmlt</a><br />\n<br />\n淨係話:<br />\nEveryone interested in technology is welcome to join.<br />\n<br />\n但無理由又乜都唔識睇住隊友做架下嘛?<br />\n<br />\n希望有試過既師兄可以分享下經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0d8d147e64cf85903dddc583fc83bfdd583c73","tid":888974,"uid":147629,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T08:18:55.000Z","msg":"開得post問已經代表唔啱你玩，玩hackathon除非早有準備，即場dup嘅team都係不停google不停睇documentation再落手砌。<br />\n<br />\n你tech background又無，google又唔識，諗起hackathon時有條煩膠問問問都覺得慘。"},{"pid":"ba8ebe721e863e648f6b8e55bdf7625c5bdfb87a","tid":888974,"uid":147629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fb0d8d147e64cf85903dddc583fc83bfdd583c73","tid":888974,"uid":147629,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T08:18:55.000Z","msg":"開得post問已經代表唔啱你玩，玩hackathon除非早有準備，即場dup嘅team都係不停google不停睇documentation再落手砌。<br />\n<br />\n你tech background又無，google又唔識，諗起hackathon時有條煩膠問問問都覺得慘。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T08:21:40.000Z","msg":"大概三大CS penultimate year + 有砌開project or有hackathon經驗，非tech底就native/near native level english speaker<br />\n<br />\n咁就唔會拖累，因為你去到就會發現一大班tech底人都係咁。"},{"pid":"b004c6602a37e76e62cd7a107dd3bcef7c8d4063","tid":888974,"uid":125976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:21:00.000Z","msg":"玩過一次，主要係我朋友想玩，係寫 game 嘅 hackathon，但玩完覺得有啲搵笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大會包三日三餐，有 sponsor，你冇心嘅話當去黐餐都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但因為佢係交 video 同 present，真係好有香港特色吹水文化，基本上你條片整得好同 present 得好就贏。好記得嗰陣仲有人整 physical 卡牌，最後好似攞到獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於我有位喺美國讀書嘅 friend 都玩過，美國嗰邊可能好少少，但都有個問題就係比賽內容係為咗 sponsor。<br />\n<br />\n例如係 Uber 做 sponsor，就要你用 Uber 嘅 API<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6719cd672273335876d818e47697dddb21d05135","tid":888974,"uid":147785,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ba8ebe721e863e648f6b8e55bdf7625c5bdfb87a","tid":888974,"uid":147629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fb0d8d147e64cf85903dddc583fc83bfdd583c73","tid":888974,"uid":147629,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T08:18:55.000Z","msg":"開得post問已經代表唔啱你玩，玩hackathon除非早有準備，即場dup嘅team都係不停google不停睇documentation再落手砌。<br />\n<br />\n你tech background又無，google又唔識，諗起hackathon時有條煩膠問問問都覺得慘。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T08:21:40.000Z","msg":"大概三大CS penultimate year + 有砌開project or有hackathon經驗，非tech底就native/near native level english speaker<br />\n<br />\n咁就唔會拖累，因為你去到就會發現一大班tech底人都係咁。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:27:00.000Z","msg":"係CU讀緊IE<br />\n<br />\nproject又唔係話成日砌既 但都有打code習慣<br />\n<br />\n主要係google左好耐都冇乜見人講 係香港hackathon既經驗 所以開post下姐<br />\n<br />\n但聽你咁講 等埋下個sem 讀多幾個CS course先再試都未遲"},{"pid":"a7a980d1b8563790be10a05b4983e88fdd6d1394","tid":888974,"uid":170252,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:29:53.000Z","msg":"hackathon其實唔洗太tech，識coding就參加得。好多嘢都係即時睇即時做。唔霖住贏未當係social event 去黐飲黐食。最重要要搵到一班相同霖法既teamate。霖住贏就另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申，玩過，贏過。"},{"pid":"5627903f2bbc540db70c01caeb9a173e0ad2b039","tid":888974,"uid":152934,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:11:45.000Z","msg":"唔識coding 去玩會唔會好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8654c6a9f84feabd05ac64ab2319fe4d4fa22f","tid":888974,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7a980d1b8563790be10a05b4983e88fdd6d1394","tid":888974,"uid":170252,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:29:53.000Z","msg":"hackathon其實唔洗太tech，識coding就參加得。好多嘢都係即時睇即時做。唔霖住贏未當係social event 去黐飲黐食。最重要要搵到一班相同霖法既teamate。霖住贏就另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申，玩過，贏過。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:24:33.000Z","msg":"ching玩果次係咩topic?"},{"pid":"95405c7f437dbbf6d2ff4b7925eba2fd5a5898e2","tid":888974,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5627903f2bbc540db70c01caeb9a173e0ad2b039","tid":888974,"uid":152934,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:11:45.000Z","msg":"唔識coding 去玩會唔會好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T13:25:13.000Z","msg":"ching有興趣?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ba712072ada1a2f3b35946fd743317ce6d647b","tid":888974,"uid":170252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f8654c6a9f84feabd05ac64ab2319fe4d4fa22f","tid":888974,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7a980d1b8563790be10a05b4983e88fdd6d1394","tid":888974,"uid":170252,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:29:53.000Z","msg":"hackathon其實唔洗太tech，識coding就參加得。好多嘢都係即時睇即時做。唔霖住贏未當係social event 去黐飲黐食。最重要要搵到一班相同霖法既teamate。霖住贏就另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申，